       <p class="intertitre"><a href="https://pangloss.cnrs.fr/corpus/show_text_en.php?id=cocoon-87d30d70-2c8d-45d1-a4ee-74d8059cb3ba&idref=cocoon-d618b966-b9fe-4bb1-bec4-de97a4c04c83"><img src="../images/icones/Txt_Inter_parchemin1.jpg" alt="a" width="30" height="30" border="0">Memories from a childhood in Sokdzong</a></p>
      
            <p>སངས་རྒྱས་མཚོ་, a woman aged 29 in 2017, was born in གསེར་ལུང་།, in the county of Sokdzong (Ch. Henan xian 河南县). She moved to the county seat at about age seven, to attend school. She studied Tibetan medicine for four years at the University in Xining (the capital of Qinghai province). In 2013, after completing her studies, she went back to the Sokdzong county seat. In addition to Tibetan, she speaks fluent Chinese.</p>
